      "para_id": "Q000940.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nanna , the firstborn child of Enlil , his master , Ur-Namma , lord of Unug , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built and restored the E-temen-ni-guru , his beloved temple ."
